title: Xolo Maridueña Taste Tests the Ultimate Stuffed Crust Pizza | Pizza Wars

media:group.media:title: Xolo Maridueña Taste Tests the Ultimate Stuffed Crust Pizza | Pizza Wars
media:group.media:description:
Eating stuffed crust pizza is like mainlining nostalgia. But what happens when you take one of the world's cheesiest dishes and stuff it with even more cheese? On an all-new episode of Pizza Wars, host Nicole Russell faces off against TikTok phenom Salvatore Mandreucci—aka Sally Slices—to see who can fit the most fillings inside their crust. Only Cobra Kai's Xolo Maridueña, and AEW professional wrestler Britt Baker, can decide if these stuffed crust creations pack enough punch.
